From 31ddeed327095d5ba170c2d9e823bbafda0c1027 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Florent Revest <revestflo@gmail.com>
Date: Thu, 30 Apr 2026 16:41:39 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 4/5] Fix build with Qt6

Some of the changes required are:
- Switching from QRegExp to QRegularExpression
- Dropping QT_BEGIN_HEADER, QT_END_HEADER
- Using a newer C++ standard
- Using new dependencies
- Using Qt features that got moved to different namespaces

Upstream-Status: Inappropriate
